&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/releases/download/v0.128.0/hugo_extended_0.128.0_windows-amd64.zip&#34;  title=&#34;Windows 64位AMD拓展版&#34;
